# Raster image-gen masters live in MinIO (docs/brand/imagery/hosting.md).
# Web JPG review copies in docs/brand/imagery/renders/web/ stay in git for
# async review without a MinIO round-trip. Prompts (*.prompt.txt) stay in
# git as the audit trail. Raw Imagen PNGs are uploaded to MinIO out-of-band
# via scripts/upload-brand-image.mjs.
docs/brand/imagery/renders/raw/*.png

# Drive sync
# Generated PDFs (co-located with their sources)
docs/brand/brand-book/*.pdf
docs/deliverables/pitch-deck/*.pdf
# Large binary assets and stale archives — live in Drive, not git
docs/**/archive/
docs/**/assets/
.sync-state.json
.superpowers/
